	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">总统竞选人吃饭的摆拍造型，不是随便来的</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-09 07:41:41 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">18</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

<a href="/articles/25171.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/25171/indexMediumPc2/25171.jpg?1460106010" alt="这家新锐“荷兰设计”店，将混搭的手艺做到了极致">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/17/medium/17.png?1411569501" alt="设计">
			<span>设计</span>
		</p>
